This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Roland Fehr mld@diefehrs.de

Project's homepage:          http://www.minidvblinux.de

Latest version available at: http://www.minidvblinux.de

See the file COPYING for license information.

Description:

  Output device that uses gstreamer


Requirements:

  vdr-2.2.0 or later.
  
  libgstreamer1.0-dev
  libglib2.0-dev
  libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-dev
  libxrender-dev
  libxcomposite-dev
  libcairo2-dev
  libxpm-dev
  

Help if there are some missing dependencies  
  
Search for missing packages

$ sudo apt-get install apt-file
$ sudo apt-file update
$ apt-file search "X11/extensions/XTest.h"
libxtst-dev: /usr/include/X11/extensions/XTest.h

Once you've the package name, install via:

sudo apt-get install libxtst-dev

